        "text": "# Features of the games\n\n- **glocal productive community-oriented (coop enterprises, associations...)**: to be played by a group of 3-8 people that actually produce together towards the same goal, and use the same production infrastructure.\n- **productive**: when people play the games, they actually produce something for their current work\n- **hybrids**: there is a printed part (board, cards, pawns,dice) and a digital part (action cards are tiny tutorials of tasks to be completed on dedicated free/opensource software). One of the objective being to practice and experience as exhaustively a new workflow (communication-wise, information-wise, organization-wise,governance-wise,economically speaking).\n"
      },
      "date": 1524931610414
